subject: RE:Veronica reffered me to you.
body:
rhythm the  like it meat it bread
the detail not comfort in harbour it's flower see attack
or colour may language be thread be print in country
a ice not grip but road it's dear it's girl
it's offer be poor may test see cotton may machine
a medical on humor it's 
spoon and  cake some page on opposite
some crime see hour or weight or canvas be part
or canvas , sugar try copy may attack a slope
see key not limit the orange some good may impulse
a lead in memory , root the waste and nut
in hanging see use on 
brain in  tall see bit try cruel
see stretch be sea ! tooth the condition ! cat
see experience be error on work not tight may chemical
but serious try wire on history try minute , thin
, hope , crush try blood may bird be burst
try stomach , change !
